snippet.title: Road to Newtopia - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Road to Newtopia, a simple fangame based on the show Amphibia and inspired by several classic games such as The Oregon Trail, Earthbound, and Kirby. 

You can get more info and download the game here:
https://krizby.itch.io/newtopia

Music taken from the Amphibia launch trailer, composed by TJ Hill:
https://soundcloud.com/tjhill/amphibia-season-1-teaser?in=tjhill/sets/amp1
